    "These collaborations could bridge the gap between theoretical knowledge and practical application, giving students a more comprehensive understanding of AI's real-world implications.",
    "However, perhaps students may have interesting ideas themselves of how a responsible culture of AI could be fostered.",
    "Encouraging student-led AI initiatives, such as projects and clubs, can motivate a hands-on learning environment.",
    "These initiatives may promote peer learning, innovation, and practical application of AI knowledge.",
    "By actively engaging in AI projects, students can develop critical thinking and problem-solving skills that are essential in navigating the complexities of an accelerating digital world."
